messages:
Name: Lucas Torreira
Nationality: Uruguay
Date of Birth: February 11, 1996
Position: Midfielder
Current club: Arsenal
Premier League clubs played for: Arsenal, Fiorentina
Lucas Torreira is an Arsenal midfielder who joined the club on June 30, 2022.
Torreira last featured in a Premier League game on May 21, 2022, playing just five minutes for Fiorentina against Juventus in a 2-0 win.
A home match against Leicester City on August 13 is the side's next Premier League fixture for Arsenal, who have three points and are top of the table.
Torreira played 31 Serie A games last season for Fiorentina, scored five goals and provided one assist.
Torreira rejoined Arsenal in June 2022 after a loan spell at Arsenal, for whom he made 63 league appearances in total, scoring three goals and providing three assists.

The midfielder debuted in a Premier League fixture for Arsenal on August 12, 2018 as a substitute versus Manchester City aged 22 years and 182 days. In his Premier League career overall, he has appeared 63 times in the competition, with three goals and three assists.
